# UIAccessibilityContainerType.dataTable

**Case**

A table that contains structured data.

## Declaration

```swift
case dataTable
```

## Discussion

To use this container type, you must also implement the [doc://com.apple.uikit/documentation/UIKit/UIAccessibilityContainerDataTable] protocol.

## Constants

- **UIAccessibilityContainerType.none**: No additional data.
- **UIAccessibilityContainerType.list**: A list of data.
- **UIAccessibilityContainerType.landmark**: Landmark data.
- **UIAccessibilityContainerType.semanticGroup**: A semantic group of data.
